@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>.
@prefix prof: <http://www.w3.org/ns/dx/prof/>.
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.

<> a owl:Ontology, prof:Profile.
<sweetResult> a owl:Class, rdfs:Class;
    rdfs:label "Sweet Result"@en;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <>.
<unevenMother> a owl:Class, rdfs:Class;
    rdfs:label "Uneven Mother"@en;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <>.
<gorgeousCommunity> a rdf:Property, owl:ObjectProperty;
    rdfs:label "Gorgeous Community"@en;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <>;
    rdfs:domain <unevenMother>;
    rdfs:range <sweetResult>.
